https://sentinel.esa.int/web/sentinel/home


please find the python jupyter notebooks to autodownload the sentinel data using the user credentials. 

how to use?

go to respective notebook for sentinel 1 or 2 data
edit the username and password
edit the .shp file/ geojson data to indicate the region of interest.
give the starting and ending date
download and enjoy.....

credits to sentinel api:)
